{"tid":2056443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突發）習近平到寧夏了解黃河生態　探望回滿蒙藏族社區居民","createTime":"2020-06-08T16:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T16:58:00.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c41c57a901a08d15cbb1075b8420a799ad624a6","tid":2056443,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"習近平到寧夏了解黃河生態　探望回滿蒙藏族社區居民<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平到寧夏考察調研。習近平前往吳忠市金星鎮金花園社區了解當地居民情況，社區內居住有回、滿、蒙、藏等少數民族，佔總人口45%。另外，習近平亦前往黃河吳忠市城區段，了解當地加強黃河流域生態保護等情況。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-09 00:23:36"},{"pid":"0dac31b82da66c02bb0f25862cea5cc49afa478c","tid":2056443,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻小學雞一遇著D咩搞唔掂就縮返去老母閪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdd17923d46e86ce43ae35c8da77368eb9df2ba","tid":2056443,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"佢個口罩一時有一時冇，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b008eb5474e45bf354a74095eb569ab7f621c9fc","tid":2056443,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"呢條仆街快啲死呀"}]}